Package io.pet.Encryption

Class Cipher

java.lang.Object
io.pet.AbstractDataPET
io.pet.Encryption.Cipher
All Implemented Interfaces:
IPET
public class Cipher
extends AbstractDataPET
This is the Cipher class. It represents a dataobject in a BPMN file that is as output of an PKEncrypt or PKComputatin task. The groupId indicates which pair of key can be use to decrypt it.
Author:
S. Belluccini
